5:5: warning: constant href value "javascript:alert(1)" on <a> always sanitizes to about:invalid#gsx at render time; allowed schemes here are http/https/mailto/tel; vouch with gsx.RawURL if this value is intentional
-- render.golden --
<img src="about:invalid#gsx" alt="x"><a href="about:invalid#gsx">x</a>
